Trademarks
----------
"Claude" and the Claude logo are trademarks of Anthropic, PBC. ClaudeOrb renders
the Claude mark only as a small on-device icon to identify what the gadget shows.
If you redistribute this project, comply with Anthropic's brand/trademark guidelines.

Bundled / adapted third-party material
--------------------------------------
* firmware/claude_orb/st77916_ws_init.h
    The ST77916 panel initialisation sequence is adapted from Waveshare's
    ESP32-S3-Touch-LCD-1.85 example code (the panel-specific "vendor" init).
    Credit: Waveshare (https://www.waveshare.com/wiki/ESP32-S3-Touch-LCD-1.85).

* firmware/claude_orb/claude_logo.h
    A small RGB565 bitmap of the Claude mark, generated by tools/gen_logo.py from
    the lobehub icon set (https://github.com/lobehub/lobe-icons, MIT). The logo
    artwork itself is a trademark of Anthropic (see above).

